For FWO, the Data Management Plan should be written using the Flemish Standard DMP template. You will notice that this requires more detailed information to be provided beyond what you have written so far.

You can write your DMP in DMPonline.be (log in with your KU Leuven credentials), where you select FWO as funder when you create a new plan to automatically generate a plan in the correct template.
Or you can use a Word template. Info here: https://www.kuleuven.be/rdm/en/guidance/dmp
